**Content:** Furthermore, unrestrained illegal immigration is contributing to an underclass culture among the children of some Hispanic illegal aliens. High school dropout rates, teen pregnancy, out-of-wedlock births, and gang involvement are alarmingly high among this demographic. A quote from an undocumented Guatemalan girl in Los Angeles illustrates this point: "Most of the students I hung out with when I started school have dropped out. Others got kicked out or got into drugs. Five graduated and four homegirls got pregnant." While many Hispanic immigrants are industrious, the assimilation of some children into an underclass will lead to increased welfare costs and crime if current levels of illegal immigration persist.
**Argument:** High school dropout rates, teen pregnancy, out-of-wedlock births, and gang involvement are alarmingly high among this demographic. A quote from an undocumented Guatemalan girl in Los Angeles illustrates the negative social outcomes. Assimilation of some children into an underclass will lead to increased welfare costs and crime if current levels of illegal immigration persist.

**Claim:** Welcoming legal immigrants who respect our laws is important, but granting the same privileges to those who flout them is detrimental to our national interest.
**Purpose:** propose => Welcoming legal immigrants who respect our laws is important, but granting the same privileges to those who flout them is detrimental to our national interest.;
**Content:** We should welcome legal immigrants who respect our laws, but it's an insult to them, and detrimental to our national interest, to grant the same privileges to those who choose to flout them.
**Argument:** It is an insult to legal immigrants who respect our laws. It is detrimental to our national interest.


